    "type": "message",
    "text": "Does anyone know of a web browser where instead of switching between tabs you can smoothly/continuously transition between websites? E.g. similar to the Eagle Mode software (see video), but for the web: where when you zoom into a link, the link grows into a website, and when you zoom out, you smoothly return to the previous web page.\nOr like a digital whiteboard (e.g. <http://conceptboard.com|conceptboard.com>), where you can put thumbnails of websites on a whiteboard, and then zoom in a thumbnail to open the website and zoom out to return back to the whiteboard.\n<https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G6yPQKt3mBA>",
